  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of oil in a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped walnuts and cook for 2 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "Add the chia seeds and cook for 1 minute, stirring frequently.",
    "Add the Greek yogurt and stir until combined with the walnuts and chia seeds.",
    "Add the cheonggukjang and stir until heated through.",
    "Add the honey, cinnamon powder, turmeric powder, and ginger powder, and stir until combined.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a bowl and serve immediately.",
